title: Jalinna Jones Receives Yellow Rose of Texas Award (Texas A&M University - Commerce)
text: ( Source : Texas A&M University - Commerce) Texas State Representative Dan Flynn surprised Jalinna Jones , Texas A&M University-Commerce First Lady , with the Yellow Rose of Texas Award today at the Lt. General Claire Lee Chennault
